
Main activity test cases
the user can enter into the school name field to be used in the search
the user can select a value from the range spinner to be used in the search
the user can select a value from the rating spinner to be used in the search
the user can enter an integer value for the monthly budget to be used in the search
the user can click the favorite icon in the menu to see all current favorites
the user can perform the search with search criteria or none at all to view schools


List activity test cases
the user can filter the list set by school name that is searched in the database
the user can view favorites, by searching for them in the database
the user can click an item to go to the details


Detail activity test cases
the user can select the school as a favorite